</P>
<P>
   A5741 BC-NH-REPUBS-DEBATE-NYT 976 22:31 U P
</P>
<P>
   MINUS BUSH, GOP HOPEFULS KICK OFF DEBATES IN NEW HAMPSHIRE
</P>
<P>
   A5739 BC-DEBATE23-COX 632 22:30 U P
</P>
<P>
   A5699 BC-BUSH-BOOK-1STLD-WRITETHRU-NYT 1026 22:05 U P
