<HEADLINE>
SEVENTY THEATERS TO GET `FANTASIA/2000'
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE MCNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   VALENCIA, CALIF. -- Santa Clarita Valley moviegoing received a
status upgrade as The Walt Disney Co. announced the Edwards Imax
