<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-POLITICS-LITERATURE-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PUBLISHING, THE MORAL MIRROR OF POLITICS 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
