u i BC-JAPAN-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-     10-23 0731
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JAPAN-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 TOKYO: be sacred.  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Another sign of change has been visible in a running fight this
year between the Bank of Japan and the Ministry of Finance _ a
result of a law that severed corrosive links between the two
institutions. Surprisingly for a country that has long kept policy
