<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-23 12:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6088 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-FRIEDMAN-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      10-23 0770
