 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   As Internet users stampeded to visit the Encyclopaedia
Britannica's sleek new Web site last week, the venerable
intellectual icon was nearly road kill on the information highway.
</P>
<P>
   Britannica.com is busily adding computers to handle the more
